description: What started as shortness of breath has turned into a solid lump in his pants. Luckily for Carter Woods, neighbour Donte Thick was just on his way out the door to work when he sees Carter struggling. Doctor Donte diagnoses a deep dick discovery to delve into Carter's dilemma, and he doesn't stop until he's done with the deed. Carter is thankful to have such a thorough onsite examination of some of his more gaping issue, and Doctor Donte is a no bullshit kind of physician, ready to give Carter the raw remedy he really requires.  Enjoy!
title: Deep Diagnosis
